      "email",
      {
        "html": "<p>Hello {first_name, \"there\"},‌‌‌‌</p><p>I'm deep in a long piece about analytics use and the newsroom, triggered by recent discussions about Reach and their analytics use. It's going to be <em>great</em>, he says immodestly. But it's not getting done today, so here's a quick look at three things that have crossed my radar in recent days that show a little of how the world if evolving around social platform use.</p><p>I hope you find it thought-provoking…</p>"
      }
    ],
    [
